%N A395544 Number of transitive relations on an n-set with at most eight ordered pairs.
%H A395544 <a href="/index/Rec#order_17">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (17,-136,680,-2380,6188,-12376,19448,-24310,24310,-19448,12376,-6188,2380,-680,136,-17,1).
%F A395544 a(n) = A395093(n) + A393925(n).
%e A395544 a(2) = 13: every transitive relation on a 2-set has at most 4 <= 8 ordered pairs, so all 13 transitive relations on [2] are counted.
%e A395544 a(3) = 170: of the 171 transitive relations on [3], only the complete relation [3] X [3] (with 9 ordered pairs) is excluded.
